<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to JobTowners</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4a6cf7;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4a6cf7;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to JobTowners!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
      <p>Thank you for joining JobTowners! We're excited to have you as part of our community.</p>
      <p>With your new account, you can:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Create and manage your professional profile</li>
        <li>Connect with employers and other professionals</li>
        <li>Apply for jobs that match your skills and interests</li>
        <li>Stay updated with the latest opportunities in your field</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To get started, simply log in to your account:</p>
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Log In to Your Account</a>
      </div>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The JobTowners Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} JobTowners. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This email was sent to you because you registered on JobTowners.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 